  "instructions": [
    "preheat the oven to 400f and prepare 4 mason jars for roasting",
    "line each jar with parchment paper and place a sea bass fillet in each",
    "in a small bowl, mix together the lemon juice, ginger paste, garam masala, coriander, turmeric, cumin, red chili powder and salt",
    "brush the spice mixture evenly over each sea bass fillet",
    "drizzle the oil over each fillet and sprinkle with a pinch of salt",
    "place the mason jars on a baking sheet and roast for 12 minutes",
    "remove from the oven and let rest for 2 minutes before serving"
  ],
